early and pursuin=\r\ng higher dharma. As a result, they may continue to allotted roles where lig=\r\nhter and lighter mental conditioning restricts them and eventually they bec=\r\nome free.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;One can try to use free will to move from the former case =\r\nto the latter case.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Best regards,&lt;br&gt;Narasimha&lt;br&gt;------------ -----=\r\n---- --------- --------- --------- --------- --------- -&lt;br&gt;&nbsp; Free\n Jy=\r\notish\n Software, Free Jyotish Lessons, Jyotish Writings,&lt;br&gt;&quot;Do It Yourself=\r\n&quot; ritual manuals for short Homam and Pitri Tarpana:&lt;br&gt;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;=\r\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;a rel=3D&quot;nofollow&quot; target=3D&quot;_b=\r\nlank&quot; href=3D&quot;http://www.vedicastrologer.org/&quot;&gt;http://www.VedicAst rologer.=\r\norg&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Films that make a difference: &lt;a rel=3D=\r\n&quot;nofollow&quot; target=3D&quot;_blank&quot; href=3D&quot;http://saraswatifilms.org/&quot;&gt;http://Sar=\r\naswatiFil ms.org&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Spirituality: &lt;a rel=3D&quot;no=\r\nfollow&quot; target=3D&quot;_blank&quot; href=3D&quot;http://groups.yahoo.com/group/vedic-wisdo=\r\nm&quot;&gt;http://groups. yahoo.com/ group/vedic- wisdom&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&nbsp; Jyotish writ=\r\nings: &lt;a rel=3D&quot;nofollow&quot; target=3D&quot;_blank&quot; href=3D&quot;http://groups.yahoo.com=\r\n/group/JyotishWritings&quot;&gt;http://groups. yahoo.com/ group/JyotishWri tings&lt;/a=\r\n&gt;&lt;br&gt;------------ --------- --------- --------- --------- --------- -------=\r\n-- -&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;---- Raj Nambisan &lt;&lt;a rel=3D&quot;nofollow&quot; target=3D&quot;_blank&quot;\n hr=\r\nef=3D&quot;http://us.mc300.mail.yahoo.com/mc/compose?to=3Drajnambisan@...&quot;=\r\n&gt;rajnambisan@ yahoo.com&lt;/a&gt;&gt;\n wrote: &lt;br&gt;&gt; namaste,&lt;br&gt;&gt;&nbsp; &lt;br=\r\n&gt;&gt; i have a question: if everyone is playing the 