d such-and-such a thing. The n=\r\next day there will be people to criticise it. Our business is to keep quiet=\r\n. If we enter into all these, people will naturally ask, and justifiably, =\r\n=E2=80=98Why is he interfering in all these instead of keeping quiet?=E2=80=\r\n=99 &lt;br&gt;&gt; &lt;br&gt;&gt; Similarly if Mahatma Gandhi keeps quiet leaving aside=\r\n all his activities,they will ask, =E2=80=98Why is he keeping quiet instead=\r\n of engaging in all these activities?=E2=80=99\n He must do what he has come=\r\n for. We must do what we have come for.=E2=80=9D&lt;br&gt;&gt; &lt;br&gt;&gt; Source: D=\r\nAY BY DAY WITH BHAGAVAN From the Diary of A. DEVARAJA MUDALIAR &lt;br&gt;&gt; &lt;br=\r\n&gt;&gt; -- &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;------------ --------- --------- ------&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;|| =\r\nOm Shaantih Shaantih Shaantih ||&lt;br&gt;Yahoo! Groups Links&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;*&gt; To=\r\n visit your group on the web, go to:&lt;br&gt;&nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;a rel=3D&quot;nofollow&quot; t=\r\narget=3D&quot;_blank&quot; href=3D&quot;http://groups.yahoo.com/group/vedic-wisdom/&quot;&gt;http:=\r\n//groups. yahoo.com/ group/vedic- wisdom/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;*&gt; Your email s=\r\nettings:&lt;br&gt;&nbsp; &nbsp; Individual Email | Traditional&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;*&gt; T=\r\no change settings online go to:&lt;br&gt;&nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;a rel=3D&quot;nofollow&quot; target=\r\n=3D&quot;_blank&quot; href=3D&quot;http://groups.yahoo.com/group/vedic-wisdom/join&quot;&gt;http:/=\r\n/groups. yahoo.com/ group/vedic- wisdom/join&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&nbsp; &nbsp; (Yahoo! I=\r\nD required)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;*&gt; To change settings via email:&lt;br&gt;&nbsp; &nbsp;=\r\n &lt;a rel=3D&quot;nofollow&quot; target=3D&quot;_blank&quot;\n href=3D&quot;http://us.mc300.mail.yahoo.=\r\ncom/mc/compose?to=3Dvedic-wisdom-digest@yahoogroups.com&quot;&gt;vedic-wisdom- dige=\r\nst@yahoogrou ps.com&lt;/a&gt; &lt;br&gt;&nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;a rel=3D&quot;nofollow&quot; t